import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Typography, Link, Grid, IconButton, Divider } from '@mui/material';
import FacebookIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Facebook';
import TwitterIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Twitter';
import InstagramIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Instagram';
import LinkedInIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LinkedIn';
import GitHubIcon from '@mui/icons-material/GitHub';
import EventNoteIcon from '@mui/icons-material/EventNote';

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      component="footer"
      sx={{
        py: 6,
        px: 2,
        mt: 8,
        backgroundColor: 'primary.main',
        color: 'white',
        backgroundImage: 'linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(67, 97, 238, 0.95) 0%, rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.95) 100%)',
        position: 'relative',
        overflow: 'hidden',
        '&::before': {
          content: '""',
          position: 'absolute',
          top: 0,
          left: 0,
          width: '100%',
          height: '100%',
          background: 'radial-gradient(circle at 20% 150%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 40%)',
          pointerEvents: 'none',
        },
      }}
    >
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="space-between">
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4} sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: { xs: 'center', md: 'flex-start' } }}>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
              <EventNoteIcon sx={{ fontSize: 32, mr: 1 }} />
              <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight="bold" letterSpacing={1}>
                SCHEDULER
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mb: 2, textAlign: { xs: 'center', md: 'left' } }}>
              Simplify your appointment booking process with our intuitive scheduling platform.
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 1 }}>
              <IconButton size="small" sx={{ color: 'white', '&:hover': { transform: 'translateY(-3px)', transition: 'transform 0.3s ease' } }}>
                <FacebookIcon />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton size="small" sx={{ color: 'white', '&:hover': { transform: 'translateY(-3px)', transition: 'transform 0.3s ease' } }}>
                <TwitterIcon />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton size="small" sx={{ color: 'white', '&:hover': { transform: 'translateY(-3px)', transition: 'transform 0.3s ease' } }}>
                <InstagramIcon />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton size="small" sx={{ color: 'white', '&:hover': { transform: 'translateY(-3px)', transition: 'transform 0.3s ease' } }}>
                <LinkedInIcon />
              </IconButton>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={6} md={2}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
              Quick Links
            </Typography>
            <Box component="ul" sx={{ listStyle: 'none', p: 0, m: 0 }}>
              <Box component="li" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                <Link href="/" color="inherit" underline="hover" sx={{ transition: 'all 0.3s ease', '&:hover': { pl: 0.5 } }}>
                  Home
                </Link>
              </Box>
              <Box component="li" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                <Link href="/dashboard" color="inherit" underline="hover" sx={{ transition: 'all 0.3s ease', '&:hover': { pl: 0.5 } }}>
                  Dashboard
                </Link>
              </Box>
              <Box component="li" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                <Link href="/calendar" color="inherit" underline="hover" sx={{ transition: 'all 0.3s ease', '&:hover': { pl: 0.5 } }}>
                  Calendar
                </Link>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={6} md={2}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
              Resources
            </Typography>
            <Box component="ul" sx={{ listStyle: 'none', p: 0, m: 0 }}>
              <Box component="li" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                <Link href="#" color="inherit" underline="hover" sx={{ transition: 'all 0.3s ease', '&:hover': { pl: 0.5 } }}>
                  Help Center
                </Link>
              </Box>
              <Box component="li" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                <Link href="#" color="inherit" underline="hover" sx={{ transition: 'all 0.3s ease', '&:hover': { pl: 0.5 } }}>
                  Privacy Policy
                </Link>
              </Box>
              <Box component="li" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                <Link href="#" color="inherit" underline="hover" sx={{ transition: 'all 0.3s ease', '&:hover': { pl: 0.5 } }}>
                  Terms of Service
                </Link>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
              Built With
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexWrap: 'wrap', gap: 1 }}>
              <Link href="https://reactjs.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" sx={{ 
                display: 'inline-flex', 
                alignItems: 'center',
                bgcolor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                color: 'white',
                px: 1.5,
                py: 0.5,
                borderRadius: 2,
                fontSize: '0.875rem',
                textDecoration: 'none',
                transition: 'all 0.3s ease',
                '&:hover': {
                  bgcolor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2)',
                  transform: 'translateY(-2px)'
                }
              }}>
                <GitHubIcon sx={{ fontSize: 16, mr: 0.5 }} /> React
              </Link>
              <Link href="https://expressjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" sx={{ 
                display: 'inline-flex', 
                alignItems: 'center',
                bgcolor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                color: 'white',
                px: 1.5,
                py: 0.5,
                borderRadius: 2,
                fontSize: '0.875rem',
                textDecoration: 'none',
                transition: 'all 0.3s ease',
                '&:hover': {
                  bgcolor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2)',
                  transform: 'translateY(-2px)'
                }
              }}>
                <GitHubIcon sx={{ fontSize: 16, mr: 0.5 }} /> Express
              </Link>
              <Link href="https://www.mongodb.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" sx={{ 
                display: 'inline-flex', 
                alignItems: 'center',
                bgcolor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                color: 'white',
                px: 1.5,
                py: 0.5,
                borderRadius: 2,
                fontSize: '0.875rem',
                textDecoration: 'none',
                transition: 'all 0.3s ease',
                '&:hover': {
                  bgcolor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2)',
                  transform: 'translateY(-2px)'
                }
              }}>
                <GitHubIcon sx={{ fontSize: 16, mr: 0.5 }} /> MongoDB
              </Link>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
        
        <Divider sx={{ my: 4, borderColor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2)' }} />
        
        <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', flexDirection: { xs: 'column', sm: 'row' } }}>
          <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mb: { xs: 1, sm: 0 } }}>
            © {new Date().getFullYear()} Appointment Scheduler. All rights reserved.
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2">
            Designed with ❤️ for better scheduling
          </Typography>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Footer;
